00:00:00,630 --> 00:00:03,610
Building means in house custom development.

2
00:00:03,610 --> 00:00:06,689
The advantages and disadvantages mirror those of buying.

3
00:00:06,689 --> 00:00:08,600
The build solution may cost you more,

4
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:12,500
because you don't have the same economies of scale that a vendor might have.

5
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:15,660
However, you can tailor what you build to your own situation.

6
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:18,970
You also retain control of its intellectual property.

7
00:00:18,970 --> 00:00:22,860
However, overall delivery risk is increased when you build things yourself.
